      "unit_kind": "feature",
      "description": "Execution bundle for a feature: its contained stories (out), its dependencies (out), and its gates (out). All stored parent=feature -> child, so they resolve as descendants. The zero-edge feature_governed_by_decision is omitted (feature_gated_by_item already reaches gating decisions); add it if/when such edges exist.",
